ajor%20victories%20have%20emboldened%20rebels%20to%20push%20south%20toward%20Homs%2C%20Syria's%20third-largest%20city%2C%20and%20even%20closer%20to%20Damascus%2C%20the%20seat%20of%20Assad's%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20rebel%20coalition%20spearheading%20this%20offensive%20is%20led%20by%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%2C%20a%20group%20with%20origins%20in%20Al-Qaeda.%20Though%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20Western%20governments%2C%20HTS%20leader%20Abu%20Mohammed%20al-Jolani%20said%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20the%20group's%20primary%20goal%20remains%20the%20overthrow%20of%20Assad.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20the%20country's%20east%2C%20government%20forces%20vacated%20Deir%20Ezzor%2C%20ceding%20territory%20to%20Kurdish-led%20Syrian%20Democratic%20Forces%20(SDF)%20backed%20by%20the%20United%20States.%20The%20withdrawal%20appears%20sudden%2C%20with%20troops%20reportedly%20regrouping%20in%20Palmyra%2C%20a%20key%20junction%20on%20the%20road%20to%20Homs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAirstrikes%20by%20Syrian%20and%20Russian%20aircraft%20have%20sought%20to%20slow%20the%20rebel%20advance%2C%20but%20observers%20note%20that%20these%20efforts%20have%20been%20relatively%20limited%2C%20likely%20reflecting%20Russia's%20stretched%20military%20commitments%20elsewhere%2C%20particularly%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EJordan%20has%20closed%20its%20border%20crossings%20with%20Syria%2C%20while%20Lebanon%20has%20imposed%20restrictions%20on%20land%20crossings.%20Israel%2C%20which%20occupies%20the%20Golan%20Heights%2C%20announced%20reinforcements%20to%20its%20aerial%20and%20ground%20forces.%20Turkey%2C%20which%20has%20supported%20elements%20of%20the%20Syrian%20opposition%2C%20expressed%20a%20mix%20of%20approval%20and%20caution%20over%20the%20rebel%20advance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-issues-midnight-advisory-over-grave-situation-in-syria-complete-details-here-7190703%23pfrom