0Gets%20Death%20Penalty%202%20Months%20After%20He%20Raped%2C%20Killed%2010-Year-Old%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2019-year-old%20man%20convicted%20of%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2010-year-old%20girl%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20South%2024%20Parganas%20district%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20death.%20Mostakin%20Sardar%20was%20arrested%20hours%20after%20the%20crime%20occurred%20in%20Mahishamari%20on%20October%205%20and%20a%20chargesheet%20was%20filed%20in%20a%20month.%20The%20trial%20was%20completed%20within%2031%20days%20and%20the%20sentencing%20was%20done%20in%20just%20over%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20court%20found%20him%20guilty%20on%20Friday%20under%20sections%20103%20(murder)%2C%2065%20(rape)%20and%2066%20(punishment%20for%20causing%20death%20or%20resulting%20in%20a%20persistent%20vegetative%20state%20of%20the%20victim)%20of%20the%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20Sanhita%20(BNS).%20Sections%20of%20the%20stringent%20Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offences%20(POCSO)%20Act%20were%20also%20added%20after%20scrutiny%20from%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20praised%20the%20fast%20delivery%20of%20justice%2C%20stating%20that%20the%20accused%20was%20sentenced%20to%20death%20within%2062%20days%20of%20the%20ghastly%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-man-arrested-for-gujarat-womans-rape-murder-turned-out-to-be-serial-killer-7127735%5C%22%3EHaryana%20Man%20Was%20Arrested%20For%20Rape-Murder.%20It%20Led%20To%20A%20Gruesome%20Discovery%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConviction%20and%20capital%20punishment%20in%20such%20a%20case%20in%20just%20over%20two%20months%20is%20unprecedented%20in%20the%20history%20of%20the%20state.%20I%20congratulate%20the%20state%20police%20and%20all%20those%20involved%20in%20the%20prosecution%20process%20for%20this%20outstanding%20achievement.%20The%20government%20has