-maharashtra-minister-chhagan-bhujbal-family-5058090%5C%22%3ECourt%20Closes%20Benami%20Assets%20Case%20Against%20Maharashtra%20Minister%20Chhagan%20Bhujbal%2C%20Family%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInvestigations%2C%20however%2C%20revealed%20none%20of%20the%20properties%20were%20registered%20in%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tribunal%20rejected%20the%20charges%20citing%20a%20lack%20of%20sufficient%20evidence.%20Stating%20that%20the%20properties%20were%20paid%20for%20using%20legitimate%20financial%20routes%2C%20it%20said%20the%20I-T%20department%20had%20failed%20to%20establish%20any%20link%20between%20benami%20properties%20and%20the%20Pawar%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20evidence%20to%20suggest%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%20or%20his%20family%20transferred%20funds%20to%20acquire%20benami%20properties...it's%20not%20that%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20Sunetra%20Pawar%2C%20and%20Parth%20Pawar%20transferred%20funds%20to%20procure%20benami%20properties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20tribunal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fajit-pawar-the-man-who-is-never-out-of-power-7134210%5C%22%3EAjit%20Pawar%2C%20The%20Man%20Who%20Is%20Never%20Out%20Of%20Power%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Prashant%20Patil%2C%20representing%20the%20politician%20and%20his%20family%2C%20said%20the%20allegations%20had%20no%20legal%20standing%20and%20that%20the%20family%20had%20not%20done%20anything%20wrong.%20Asserting%20that%20the%20transactions%20for%20acquiring%20these%20properties%20were%20done%20through%20legitimate%20channels%2C%20including%20the%20banking%20system%2C%20he%20said%20the%20records%20had%20no%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733546580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F21g20hf8_-ajit-pawar-pti-650_650x400_05_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbig-relief-for-ajit-pawar-