tle%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Don't%20Look%20Beyond%20Bumrah%20For%20Next%20India%20Test%20Captain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F79qqrau_bumrah_625x300_07_December_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20very%20exciting%20time%20for%20Indian%20cricket.%20The%20possibility%20of%20a%20third%20straight%20World%20Test%20Championship%20final%20beckons%2C%20along%20with%20the%20chance%20of%20completing%20a%20hat-trick%20of%20Test%20series%20wins%20in%20Australia%2C%20the%20supply%20line%20of%20talented%20players%20across%20formats%20seems%20to%20be%20very%20healthy%2C%20India%20are%20the%20reigning%20T20%20World%20champions%20and%20occupy%20the%20top%20spot%20in%20the%20ICC%20ODI%20and%20T20%20team%20rankings%2C%20along%20with%20the%20second%20spot%20in%20the%20Test%20listings%2C%20the%20IPL%20is%20going%20from%20strength%20to%20strength%2C%20and%20an%20Indian%20is%20the%20ICC%20Chairman%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20those%20of%20you%20who%20like%20to%20look%20ahead%20though%2C%20there's%20no%20doubt%20that%20the%20question%20%E2%80%98Who%20should%20be%20India's%20next%20Test%20captain%20after%20Rohit%20Sharma%3F'%20has%20crossed%20your%20mind.%20Sometimes%2C%20in%20life%2C%20the%20obvious%20choice%20is%20not%20the%20best%20one.%20In%20this%20case%20though%2C%20the%20obvious%20choice%20is%20just%20so%20appealing%20that%20it's%20difficult%20to%20look%20beyond%20it.%20In%20the%20absence%20of%20the%20captain%2C%20the%20vice-captain%20(usually)%20steps%20up%20to%20lead%20the%20team.%20As%20and%20when%20Rohit%20retires%20from%20Test%20cricket%2C%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20should%20look%20at%20following%20the%20same%2C%20simple%20formula%20to%20pick%20the%20next%20long-term%20Indian%20Test%20captain.%20Look%20no%20further%20than%20vice-captain%20Jasprit%20Bumrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESplit%20Captaincy%20A%20Constant%20Now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20delving%20into%20why%20Bumrah%20is%20the%20ideal%20Test%20captaincy%20option%2C%20let's%20also%20address%20a%20question%20that%20you%20might%20be%20asking%20right%20now%3A%20is%20split%20captaincy%20going%20to%20be%20a%20constant%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20going%20forward%3F%20Well%2C%20as%20things%20stand%2C%20it%20very%20much%20does%20look%20like%20that.%20It%20will%20be%20interesting%20to%20see%20who%20the%20Indian%20Board%20thinks%20is%20best%20suited%20for%20ODI%20captaincy%20once%20Rohit%20retires%20from%20that%20format%20or%20altogether%20from%20international%20cricket.%20Will%20the%20duties%20for%20ODI%20stewardship%20also%20be%20handed%20to%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%2C%20whose%20overall%20fitness%20and%20availability%20is%20what%20made%20the%20selectors%20pick%20him%20as%20(what%20looks%20like)%20India's%20long-term%20T20I%20captain%20ahead%20of%20Hardik%20Pandya%3F%20But%20these%20are%20questions%20for%20later.%20As%20far%20as%20the%20Test%20format%20is%20concerned%2C%20it%20would%20be%20silly%20to%20look%20at%20anyone%20else%20but%20Bumrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20all%20my%20experience%20of%20covering%20Indian%20and%20global%20sports%2C%20the%20one%20golden%20rule%20that%20emerged%20(and%20one%20that%20cuts%20across%20all%20lines%20of%20work)%20is%20that%20a%20sure-shot%20way%20of%20being%20a%20good%20leader%20is%20to%20lead%20by%20example.%20Set%20the%20bar%20high.%20Anyone%20worth%20his%20or%20her%20salt%20will%20tell%20you%20the%20same.%20Respect%20cannot%20be%20bought%2C%20it%20has%20to%20be%20earned.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20leading%20a%20cricket%20team%2C%20a%20captain%20has%20to%20be%20many%20things%3A%20a%20good%20man%2Fwoman%20manager%2C%20a%20good%20communicator%2C%20a%20shrewd%20strategist%2C%20a%20good%20listener%2C%20a%20quick%20thinker%20capable%20of%20drawing%20up%20on-the-spot%20plans%20if%20things%20aren't%20going%20right%2C%20supportive%2C%20encouraging%2C%20lively%2C%20polite%2C%20not%20over-the-top%20and%20yet%20not%20a%20pushover.%20Along%20with%20all%20this%2C%20a%20captain%20should%20be%20someone%20who%20stands%20out%20in%20terms%20of%20his%2Fher%20own%20performance%20on%20the%20field.%20And%20that%20is%20what%20works%20most%20in%20Bumrah's%20favour.%20That%20is%20what%20we%20saw%20in%20the%20Perth%20Test%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Reflection%20Of%20Another%20Great%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20casual%20look%20at%20the%20scorecard%20from%20that%20match%2C%20which%20India%20won%20by%20a%20dominating%20margin%20of%20295%20runs%2C%20shows%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20listed%20as%20the%20Man%20of%20the%20Match%20for%20his%20match%20figures%20of%208%2F72.%20Though%20that%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20properly%20encapsulate%20the%20impact%20he%20had%20on%20the%20match.%20Test%20cricket%20is%20the%20longest%20format%20of%20the%20game%20and%20unlike%20T20%20or%20even%20ODI%20cricket%2C%20you%20don't%20find%20too%20many%20matches%20that%20tilt%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20one%20team%20decisively%2C%20in%20large%20part%20because%20of%20the%20efforts%20of%20one%20player.%20That%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20impact%20Bumrah%20had%20in%20Perth.%20But%20then%2C%20he%20is%20that%20kind%20of%20rarity%E2%80%93someone%20who%20can%20take%20the%20pitch%20and%20the%20conditions%20entirely%20out%20of%20the%20equation%20to%20deliver%20body%20blow%20after%20body%20blow%20till%20the%20opposition%20is%20reeling%20and%20ready%20to%20be%20knocked%20out.%20A%20lot%20like%20the%20great%20Kapil%20Dev%2C%20whom%20Bumrah%20has%20been%20compared%20to%20quite%20a%20bit%20of%20late.%20The%20comparisons%2C%20however%2C%20are%20fruitless%2C%20because%20the%20eras%2C%20the%20rules%2C%20the%20fast%20bowling%20supporting%20cast%2C%20their%20bowling%20actions%2C%20are%20all%20different.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20cannot%20be%20debated%20though%20is%20that%20Bumrah%20could%20well%20become%20one%20of%20the%20all-time%20greats%2C%20just%20like%20Kapil%20Dev.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20not%20a%20dissection%20of%20how%20great%20a%20bowler%20Bumrah%20is%2C%20but%20an%20attempt%20to%20look%20at%20the%20facts%20at%20our%20disposal%20that%20suggest%20that%20he%20is%20a%20very%2C%20very%20good%20long-term%20Test%20captaincy%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Way%20With%20The%20Ball%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20you%20might%20have%20forgotten%20that%20Bumrah%20had%20worn%20the%20captain's%20armband%20in%20Tests%20once%20before%20as%20well.%20In%20the%202022%20Birmingham%20Test%20vs%20England%2C%20Bumrah%20led%20the%20team%20as%20Rohit%20was%20recovering%20from%20COVID-19.%20India%20lost%20that%20match%20by%20seven%20wickets%2C%20but%20Bumrah%20was%20the%20leading%20Indian%20wicket-taker%2C%20with%20five%20scalps.%20In%20England's%20second%20innings%2C%20which%20was%20dominated%20by%20centuries%20by%20Joe%20Root%20(142*)%20and%20Jonny%20Bairstow%20(114*)%2C%20Bumrah%20was%20the%20only%20one%20amongst%20the%20wickets%2C%20castling%20Zak%20Crawley%20for%2046%20and%20having%20Ollie%20Pope%20caught%20behind%20for%20a%20duck.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20his%20heroics%20with%20the%20ball%E2%80%94albeit%20in%20a%20losing%20cause%E2%80%94what%20stood%20out%20were%20Bumrah's%20comments%20when%20asked%20about%20captaincy%20before%20the%20match%3A%20%E2%80%9CGetting%20such%20an%20opportunity%20is%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20achievements%20of%20my%20career%E2%80%A6%20nothing%20changes%20for%20me%2C%20you%20have%20to%20do%20the%20job.%E2%80%9D%20The%20comments%20were%20a%20healthy%20mix%20of%20honesty%2C%20humility%2C%20practicality%20and%20job%20awareness.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20quintessentially%20Bumrah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaking%20Others%20Comfortable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20that%2C%20along%20with%20his%20almost%20superhuman%20abilities%20to%20make%20a%20cricket%20ball%20dance%20to%20his%20tunes%2C%20is%20his%20other%20big%20strength.%20He%20is%20mostly%20a%20down-to-earth%20person%2C%20largely%20humble%2C%20respected%20and%20admired%20by%20seniors%20and%20juniors%20alike%2C%20ready%20to%20whisper%20that%20extra%20word%20of%20encouragement%20in%20a%20fellow%20bowler's%20ear%2C%20and%20also%20ready%20to%20listen%2C%20collate%20and%20learn.%20Any%20player%20who%20thinks%20he%20or%20she%20knows%20it%20all%20is%20doomed%20to%20fail.%20It%20applies%20all%20the%20more%20to%20leaders.%20They%20must%20always%20be%20ready%20to%20learn%2C%20not%20just%20from%20those%20with%20more%20experience%2C%20but%20sometimes%20even%20from%20those%20who%20fall%20in%20the%20%E2%80%98junior'%20bracket.%20Here%20I%20am%20reminded%20of%20a%20few%20scenes%20from%20the%20Indian%20dressing%20room%20in%20the%20Perth%20Test%20this%20time%2C%20when%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20and%20KL%20Rahul%20were%20wearing%20down%20the%20Aussie%20bowlers%20in%20India's%20second%20innings.%20When%20the%20director%20asked%20for%20the%20feed%20to%20cut%20to%20one%20of%20the%20cameras%20focussed%20on%20the%20Indian%20dressing%20room%2C%20we%20witnessed%20just%20how%20cordially%20and%20patiently%20Bumrah%20was%20listening%20to%20and%20then%20conversing%20with%20debutante%20Harshit%20Rana.%20The%20body%20language%20of%20a%20debutante%20in%20the%20dressing%20room%20tells%20a%20million%20stories%20about%20how%20comfortable%20he%20or%20she%20is%20feeling.%20Virat%20Kohli%20is%20a%20similar%20leading%20figure%E2%80%94always%20ready%20to%20advise%20and%20guide%E2%80%94he%20has%20remained%20the%20same%20even%20after%20his%20captaincy%20spell.%20It%20wasn't%20really%20a%20surprise%20then%20to%20hear%20Rana%20say%20that%20%E2%80%98Jassi%20bhai'%20and%20%E2%80%98Virat%20bhai'%20were%20the%20two%20players%20who%20gave%20him%20%E2%80%98a%20different%20kind%20of%20confidence'%20in%20his%20very%20first%20Test%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20Bumrah%20does%20go%20on%20to%20become%20India's%20full-time%20Test%20captain%2C%20he%20will%20in%20many%20ways%20be%20a%20trendsetter.%20The%20only%20other%20fast-bowling%20captain%20India%20has%20had%20in%20Test%20cricket%20has%20been%20Kapil%20Dev%2C%20who%20belongs%20to%20that%20rare%20breed%20of%20complete%20all-rounders.%20The%20likes%20of%20Shaun%20Pollock%2C%20Ben%20Stokes%20and%20to%20an%20extent%20Imran%20Khan%20(six%20Test%20centuries)%2C%20Wasim%20Akram%20(three%20Test%20centuries)%20and%20Jason%20Holder%20(three%20Test%20centuries)%20have%20also%20been%20genuine%20all-rounder%20captains.%20Bumrah%20is%20an%20out-and-out%20fast%20bowler.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Bowlers%20Make%20Good%20Captains%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThroughout%20the%20history%20of%20the%20sport%2C%20there%20has%20been%20some%20mental%20block%20towards%20appointing%20bowlers%20as%20captains.%20Batters%20have%20always%20been%20the%20preferred%20choice.%20This%20has%20presumably%20been%20because%20a%20batter's%20overall%20workload%20allows%20them%20to%20spend%20more%20time%20to%20strategise.%20However%2C%20it's%20a%20bowler%20who%20lives%20through%20the%20changing%20nature%20of%20the%20pitch%2C%20who%20knows%20best%20what%20bowling%20strategy%20to%20adopt%20when%20and%20from%20which%20end.%20It%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20tactical%20sense%20to%20have%20a%20bowler%20as%20a%20captain.%20Also%2C%20when%20a%20fast%20bowler%20is%20made%20captain%2C%20the%20decision%20comes%20with%20the%20unsaid%20and%20unwritten%20rider%20that%20he%20or%20she%20needs%20to%20be%20careful%20about%20how%20much%20they%20are%20bowling%20themselves%20vis-%C3%A0-vis%20the%20other%20bowlers.%20Neither%20too%20much%20nor%20too%20little%20is%20acceptable.%20The%20same%20was%20a%20big%20talking%20point%20when%20Pat%20Cummins%20was%20appointed%20as%20Australia's%20Test%20and%20ODI%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20strange%20thing%20to%20worry%20about%2C%20really.%20Who%20would%20want%20to%20bowl%20themselves%20if%20they%20are%20not%20fresh%3F%20Who%20would%20realistically%20not%20throw%20the%20ball%20to%20another%20bowler%20who%20can%20possibly%20get%20a%20breakthrough%3F%20Isn't%20winning%20the%20match%20for%20the%20team%20of%20paramount%20importance%2C%20always%3F%20Bumrah%20was%20quizzed%20about%20the%20same%20before%20the%20Perth%20Test%20and%20his%20response%20to%20that%20was%20emphatic%E2%80%94%E2%80%9CI%20can%20manage%20myself%20the%20best%20when%20I%20am%20the%20captain%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cb%3EWhy%20Selectors%20Trust%20Him%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManaging%20injuries%20is%20another%20challenge%20altogether%2C%20and%20Bumrah%20has%20dealt%20with%20his%20fair%20share%20of%20that%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%20Lower%20back%20stress%20fractures%20kept%20him%20on%20the%20sidelines%20for%2011%20months.%20But%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20he%20was%20cleared%20to%20play%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20captain%20of%20the%20B-team%20that%20toured%20Ireland%20for%20three%20T20Is.%20India%20won%20the%20series%202-0%20(the%20third%20T20I%20was%20washed%20out).%20Bumrah%20was%20adjudged%20player%20of%20the%20series%20for%20his%20four%20wickets%20at%20an%20average%20of%209.75.%20There's%20a%20visible%20trust%20that%20the%20selectors%20place%20in%20his%20leadership%20abilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20he%20is%20the%20vice-captain%20of%20the%20Test%20team%20and%20the%20pace%20spearhead%2C%20and%20his%20complete%20focus%20will%20be%20on%20helping%20his%20team%20complete%20a%20third%20straight%20Test%20series%20win%20Down%20Under.%20But%20when%20the%20time%20comes%2C%20let's%20hope%20the%20powers%20that%20be%20don't%20look%20beyond%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20as%20India's%20next%20Test%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%20a%20former%20sports%20editor%20and%20primetime%20sports%20news%20anchor.%20He%20is%20currently%20a%20columnist%2C%20features%20writer%20and%20stage%20actor)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733545680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F26ka8pn8_bumrah_625x300_07_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdont-look-beyond-jasprit-bumrah-for-next-india-test-captain-7191849%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20Bumrah%20does%20go%20on%20to%20become%20Indias%20full-time%20Test%20captain%2C%20he%20will%20in%20many%20ways%20be%20a%20trendsetter.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fdont-look-beyond-jasprit-bumrah-for-next-india-test-captain-7191849%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Princess%20Kate%20Middleton%20hosts%20'Together%20at%20Christmas'%20service%2C%20her%20first%20major%20public%20event%20after%20cancer%20diagnosis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733545453000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116064422%2Cimgsize-988333.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fuk%2Fprincess-kate-middleton-hosts-together-at-christmas-service-her-first-major-public-event-after-cancer-diagnosis%2Farticleshow%2F116064415.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116064415.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EPrincess%20Kate%20returned%20to%20public%20life%2C%20hosting%20her%20annual%20Christmas%20carol%20service%20at%20Westminster%20Abbey%20after%20battling%20cancer.%20The%20service%2C%20attended%20by%20family%2C%20royals%2C%20and%20community%20members%2C%20emphasized%20love%20and%20empathy.%20Kate's%20appearance%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20in%20her%20recovery%20following%20chemotherapy%20and%20surgery%20earlier%20this%20year.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiat