Sprawling%20Investigation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECamera%20footage%20showed%20the%20suspect%20fleeing%20on%20foot%2C%20before%20getting%20on%20a%20bicycle%20--%20which%20police%20initially%20said%20may%20have%20been%20a%20rented%20e-bike.%20Police%20said%20he%20went%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20Central%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELaw%20enforcement%20sources%20said%20the%20suspected%20shooter%20traveled%20to%20New%20York%20via%20bus%20last%20month%20from%20Atlanta%2C%20Georgia%20--%20a%20distance%20of%20870%20miles%20(1%2C400%20kilometers)%2C%20according%20to%20US%20media%20Thursday.%20An%20NYPD%20spokesman%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENYPD%20chief%20of%20detectives%20Joseph%20Kenny%20would%20not%20confirm%20reports%20that%20a%20silencer%20was%20used%20on%20the%20murder%20weapon%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20question%20would%20be%20part%20of%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficers%20have%20confirmed%20that%20a%20cell%20phone%20as%20well%20as%20DNA%20from%20a%20coffee%20cup%20had%20been%20recovered%20from%20the%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20absence%20of%20an%20arrest%2C%20speculation%20has%20been%20rife%20that%20the%20gunman%20may%20have%20sought%20to%20take%20revenge%20for%20adverse%20medical%20coverage%20decisions%20made%20by%20the%20insurer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThompson's%20wife%20Paulette%20Thompson%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Minnesota%2C%20told%20NBC%20News%20that%20he%20had%20received%20unspecified%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20had%20been%20some%20threats%20basically%20I%20don't%20know%20--%20(over)%20a%20lack%20of%20coverage%3F%20I%20don't%20know%20details%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Thompson%2C%20who%20had%20two%20children%20with%20her%20late%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20UnitedHealth%20Group%2C%20the%20parent%20company%20of%20UHC%2C%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20saddened%20and%20shocked.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnitedHealthcare%20is%20a%