Ban%20After%20Losing%20Court%20Appeal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20US%20federal%20appeals%20court%20on%20Friday%20upheld%20a%20law%20requiring%20Chinese-based%20ByteDance%20to%20divest%20its%20popular%20short%20video%20app%20TikTok%20in%20the%20United%20States%20by%20early%20next%20year%20or%20face%20a%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20is%20a%20win%20for%20the%20Justice%20Department%20and%20opponents%20of%20the%20Chinese-owned%20app%20and%20a%20devastating%20blow%20to%20ByteDance.%20The%20ruling%20now%20increases%20the%20possibility%20of%20an%20unprecedented%20ban%20in%20just%20six%20weeks%20on%20a%20social%20media%20app%20used%20by%20170%20million%20Americans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20appealed%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFree%20speech%20advocates%20immediately%20criticized%20the%20decision.%20The%20American%20Civil%20Liberties%20Union%20said%20it%20sets%20a%20%26quot%3Bflawed%20and%20dangerous%20precedent.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBanning%20TikTok%20blatantly%20violates%20the%20First%20Amendment%20rights%20of%20millions%20of%20Americans%20who%20use%20this%20app%20to%20express%20themselves%20and%20communicate%20with%20people%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Patrick%20Toomey%2C%20deputy%20director%20of%20the%20ACLU's%20National%20Security%20Project.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20appeals%20court%20said%20the%20law%20%26quot%3Bwas%20the%20culmination%20of%20extensive%2C%20bipartisan%20action%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20by%20successive%20presidents.%20It%20was%20carefully%20crafted%20to%20deal%20only%20with%20control%20by%20a%20foreign%20adversary%2C%20and%20it%20was%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20effort%20to%20counter%20a%20well-substantiated%20national%20security%20threat%20posed%20by%20the%20PRC%20(People's%20Republic%20of%20China).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20appeals%20court%20Judges%20Sri%20Srinivasan%2C%20Neomi%20Rao%20and%20Douglas%20Ginsburg%20considered%20the%20legal%20challenges%20brought%20by%20TikTok%20and%20users%20against%20the%20law%20that%20gives%20ByteDance%20until%20Jan.%2019%20to%20sell%20or%20divest%20TikTok's%20US%20assets%20or%20face%20a%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20--%20unless%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20reverses%20it%20--%20puts%20TikTok's%20fate%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20first%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20whether%20to%20grant%20a%2090-day%20extension%20of%20the%20Jan.%2019%20deadline%20to%20force%20a%20sale%20and%20then%20President-elect%20Donald%20Trump%2C%20who%20takes%20office%20on%20Jan.%2020.%20But%20it's%20not%20clear%20whether%20ByteDance%20could%20meet%20the%20heavy%20burden%20to%20show%20it%20had%20made%20significant%20progress%20toward%20a%20divestiture%20needed%20to%20trigger%20the%20extension.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%2C%20who%20unsuccessfully%20tried%20to%20ban%20TikTok%20during%20his%20first%20term%20in%202020%2C%20said%20before%20the%20November%20presidential%20election%20he%20would%20not%20allow%20the%20TikTok%20ban.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20said%20it%20expected%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20would%20reverse%20the%20appeals%20court%20decision%20on%20First%20Amendment%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20an%20established%20historical%20record%20of%20protecting%20Americans'%20right%20to%20free%20speech%2C%20and%20we%20expect%20they%20will%20do%20just%20that%20on%20this%20important%20constitutional%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20TikTok%20said%20in%20a%20statement%2C%20adding%20the%20law%20will%20result%20%26quot%3Bin%20outright%20censorship%20of%20the%20American%20people.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20did%20not%20have%20an%20immediate%20comment%20on%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20upholds%20the%20law%20giving%20the%20U.S.%20government%20sweeping%20powers%20to%20ban%20other%20foreign-owned%20apps%20that%20could%20raise%20concerns%20about%20collection%20of%20Americans'%20data.%20In%202020%2C%20Trump%20also%20tried%20to%20ban%20Tencent-owned%20WeChat%2C%20but%20was%20blocked%20by%20the%20courts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20Meta%20Platforms%2C%20which%20competes%20against%20TikTok%20in%20online%20ads%2C%20hit%20an%20intraday%20record%20high%20following%20the%20ruling%2C%20last%20up%20over%203%25.%20Google%20parent%20Alphabet%2C%20whose%20YouTube%20video%20platform%20also%20competes%20with%20TikTok%2C%20was%20up%20over%201%25%20following%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETIKTOK%20BAN%20LOOMS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20acknowledged%20its%20decision%20would%20lead%20to%20TikTok's%20ban%20on%20Jan.%2019%20without%20an%20extension%20from%20Biden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConsequently%2C%20TikTok's%20millions%20of%20users%20will%20need%20to%20find%20alternative%20media%20of%20communication%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said%2C%20which%20was%20because%20of%20China's%20%26quot%3Bhybrid%20commercial%20threat%20to%20U.S.%20national%20security%2C%20not%20to%20the%20U.S.%20Government%2C%20which%20engaged%20with%20TikTok%20through%20a%20multi-year%20process%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20find%20an%20alternative%20solution.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opinion%20was%20written%20by%20Ginsburg%2C%20an%20appointee%20of%20President%20Ronald%20Reagan%2C%20and%20joined%20by%20Rao%2C%20who%20was%20named%20to%20the%20bench%20by%20Trump%2C%20and%20Srinivasan%2C%20an%20appointee%20of%20President%20Barack%20Obama.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Justice%20Department%20says%20under%20Chinese%20ownership%2C%20TikTok%20poses%20a%20serious%20national%20security%20threat%20because%20of%20its%20access%20to%20vast%20personal%20data%20of%20Americans%2C%20asserting%20China%20can%20covertly%20manipulate%20information%20that%20Americans%20consume%20via%20TikTok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EU.S.%20officials%20have%20also%20warned%20TikTok's%20management%20is%20beholden%20to%20the%20Chinese%20government%2C%20which%20could%20compel%20the%20company%20to%20share%20the%20data%20of%20its%20American%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20has%20denied%20it%20has%20or%20ever%20would%20share%20U.S.%20user%20data%2C%20accusing%20American%20lawmakers%20in%20the%20lawsuit%20of%20advancing%20%26quot%3Bspeculative%26quot%3B%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETikTok%20and%20ByteDance%20argue%20the%20law%20is%20unconstitutional%20and%20violates%20Americans'%20free%20speech%20rights.%20They%20call%20it%20%26quot%3Ba%20radical%20departure%20from%20this%20country's%20tradition%20of%20championing%20an%20open%20Internet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByteDance%2C%20backed%20by%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20Susquehanna%20International%20Group%2C%20KKR%20%26amp%3B%20Co%2C%20and%20General%20Atlantic%2C%20among%20others%2C%20was%20valued%20at%20%24268%20billion%20in%20December%202023%20when%20it%20offered%20to%20buy%20back%20around%20%245%20billion%20worth%20of%20shares%20from%20investors%2C%20Reuters%20reported%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20prohibits%20app%20stores%20like%20Apple%20and%20Alphabet's%20Google%20from%20offering%20TikTok%20and%20bars%20internet%20hosting%20services%20from%20supporting%20TikTok%20unless%20ByteDance%20divests%20TikTok%20by%20the%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApple%20and%20Google%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20concurring%20opinion%2C%20Srinivasan%20acknowledged%20the%20decision%20will%20have%20major%20impacts%2C%20noting%20%26quot%3B170%20million%20Americans%20use%20TikTok%20to%20create%20and%20view%20all%20sorts%20of%20free%20expression%20and%20engage%20with%20one%20another%20and%20the%20world.%20And%20yet%2C%20in%20part%20precisely%20because%20of%20the%20platform's%20expansive%20reach%2C%20Congress%20and%20multiple%20Presidents%20determined%20that%20divesting%20it%20from%20(China's)%20control%20is%20essential%20to%20protect%20our%20national%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3BBecause%20the%20record%20reflects%20that%20Congress's%20decision%20was%20considered%2C%20consistent%20with%20longstanding%20regulatory%20practice%2C%20and%20devoid%20of%20an%20institutional%20aim%20to%20suppress%20particular%20messages%20or%20ideas%2C%20we%20are%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20set%20it%20aside.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733543580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Feevdgq2_tiktok_625x300_07_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-appeals-court-upholds-tiktok-law-forcing-its-sale-7190421%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20federal%20appeals%20court%20on%20Friday%20upheld%20a%20law%20requiring%20Chinese-based%20ByteDance%20to%20divest%20its%20popular%20short%20video%20app%20TikTok%20in%20the%20United%20States%20by%20early%20next%20year%20or%20face%20a%20ban.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-appeals-court-upholds-tiktok-law-forcing-its-sale-7190421%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHe%20Didn't%20Have%20Talent%20In...%26quot%3B%3A%20Dravid's%20Old%20Assessment%20Of%20Kambli%20Resurfaces%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20video%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Vinod%20Kambli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F40954-vinod-ganpat-kambli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EVinod%20Kambli%3C%2Fa%3E's%20recent%20public%20appearance%20came%20to%20the%20fore%2C%20an%20old%20clip%20of%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rahul%20Dravid%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F174-rahul-dravid-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERahul%20Dravid%3C%2Fa%3E%20sharing%20his%20views%20on%20the%20definition%20of%20'talent'%2C%20while%20mentioning