20process%2C%20I%20caused%20anxiety%20and%20inconvenience%20to%20the%20public.%20I%20sincerely%20apologize%20to%20the%20citizens%20who%20were%20greatly%20distressed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20and%20key%20members%20of%20his%20own%20party%20have%20called%20for%20him%20to%20step%20down%2C%20and%20parliament%20is%20set%20to%20vote%20later%20Saturday%20on%20his%20impeachment%2C%20although%20opposition%20leader%20Lee%20Jae-myung%20told%20AFP%20it%20was%20not%20clear%20the%20motion%20could%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20said%20they%20expect%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20anti-Yoon%20protesters%20to%20take%20to%20the%20streets%20ahead%20of%20the%20vote%2C%20with%20organisers%20hoping%20200%2C000%20people%20will%20attend.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYoon%20did%20not%20offer%20to%20resign%20in%20his%20brief%20address%2C%20saying%20only%20that%20he%20would%20%26quot%3Bentrust%20the%20party%20with%20measures%20to%20stabilise%20the%20political%20situation%2C%20including%20my%20term%20in%20office.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20People%20Power%20Party%20(PPP)%20is%20divided%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20with%20lawmakers%20late%20Friday%20sticking%20to%20the%20official%20line%20that%20they%20would%20block%20impeachment%2C%20even%20after%20party%20head%20Han%20Dong-hoon%20said%20Yoon%20must%20go%20or%20Seoul%20risked%20more%20political%20chaos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20normal%20performance%20of%20the%20president's%20duties%20is%20impossible%20under%20the%20(current)%20circumstances%2C%20and%20an%20early%20resignation%20of%20the%20president%20is%20inevitable%2C%26quot%3B%20Han%20Dong-hoon%20told%20reporters%20early%20Saturday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20bloc%20holds%20192%20seats%20in%20the%20300-strong%20parliament%2C%20while%20Yoon's%20PPP%20has%20108.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%20eight%20ruling%20party%20lawmakers%20need%20to%20defect%20for%20the%20vote%20to%20get%20the%20two-thirds%20majority%20it%20needs%20to%20pass.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%