Url%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Accuses%20BJP%20Of%20'Voter%20Deletion'%20Conspiracy%2C%20Party%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAAP%20national%20convenor%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20Friday%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20orchestrating%20large-scale%20deletions%20of%20voters'%20names%20from%20the%20electoral%20rolls%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20claimed%20that%20BJP%20leaders%20had%20submitted%20applications%20to%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20to%20remove%20thousands%20of%20voter%20names%20from%20constituencies%20like%20Shahdara%2C%20Janakpuri%2C%20and%20Laxmi%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECiting%20the%20example%20of%20Shahdara%2C%20Kejriwal%20alleged%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20applied%20to%20delete%2011%2C018%20voter%20names%20from%20the%20constituency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20randomly%20checked%20500%20of%20these%20names%2C%20we%20found%20that%2075%20percent%20of%20the%20people%20are%20still%20residing%20at%20the%20listed%20addresses.%20This%20is%20nothing%20but%20an%20attempt%20to%20manipulate%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20leader%20connected%20the%20alleged%20deletions%20to%20the%20saffron%20party's%20narrow%20victory%20in%20Shahdara%20during%20the%202020%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20where%20AAP%20won%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20just%205%2C294%20votes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20removing%2011%2C000%20voters%20--%20about%206%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20total%20electorate%20in%20the%20constituency%20--%20could%20significantly%20affect%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20district%20magistrate%20of%20Shahdara%20refuted%20Kejriwal's%20claims%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BOnly%20494%20Form%207%20(deletion%20application)%20requests%20have%20been%20received%20in%20the%20Shahdara%20constituency%20since%20October%2029%2C%202024.%20The%20claim%20of%2011%2C018%20deletion%20requests%20is%20factually%20incorrect.%26quot%3B%20To%20support%20his%20allegations%2C%20Kejriwal%20presented%20several%20individuals%20at%20the%20press%20conference%2C%20whose%20names%20he%20claimed%20were%20targeted%20for%20deletion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20voters%20are%20alive%20and%20continue%20to%20live%20at%20the%20same%20addresses%20listed%20on%20the%20voter%20rolls.%20For%20instance%2C%20Upendra%20Kumar%20resides%20at%20A-334%2C%20Uma%20Devi%20at%20B-8%20Ambedkar%20Nagar%2C%20and%20Sunil%20Kumar%20at%20B-326%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi%20BJP%20president%20Virendra%20Sachdeva%20dismissed%20Kejriwal's%20allegations%20as%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%26quot%3B%20and%20accused%20AAP%20of%20shielding%20fraudulent%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRohingyas%20and%20Bangladeshis%20are%20being%20caught%2C%20and%20Kejriwal%20is%20panicking%20because%20this%20vote%20bank%2C%20funded%20by%20money%20he%20allegedly%20receives%20from%20foreign%20sources%2C%20is%20being%20exposed%2C%26quot%3B%20Sachdeva%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20greatest%20strength%20of%20Indian%20democracy%20is%20free%20speech%2C%20but%20the%20baseless%20comments%20made%20against%20constitutional%20institutions%20need%20to%20be%20examined.%26quot%3B%20Kejriwal%20also%20accused%20the%20ECI%20of%20%26quot%3Bsecretly%20processing%20deletion%20requests%20without%20transparency.%26quot%3B%20He%20called%20for%20all%20deletion%20applications%20to%20be%20published%20on%20the%20ECI%20website%20and%20demanded%20a%20halt%20to%20deletions%20initiated%20after%20October%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20response%20from%20the%20Delhi%20Chief%20Electoral%20Officer%20regarding%20the%20allegations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20the%20voter%20deletions%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%20to%20disenfranchise%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20knows%20it%20is%20losing%20the%20elections%2C%20which%20is%20why%20it%20is%20resorting%20to%20such%20unfair%20tactics.%26quot%3B%20He%20warned%20of%20legal%20action%20against%20officials%20involved%20in%20any%20irregularities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20scheduled%20for%20February%2C%20are%20crucial%20for%20AAP%2C%20which%20is%20seeking%20a%20third%20consecutive%20term%20after%20securing%20a%20landslide%20victory%20in%202020%2C%20winning%2062%20out%20of%2070%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733538300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fdfhh6qg_arvind-kejriwal-pti-_625x300_01_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-accuses-bjp-of-voter-deletion-conspiracy-party-responds-7191405%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AAP%20national%20convenor%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20on%20Friday%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20orchestrating%20large-scale%20deletions%20of%20voters'%20names%20from%20the%20electoral%20rolls%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Assembly%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwal-accuses-bjp-of-voter-deletion-conspiracy-party-responds-7191405%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'I%20don't%20know%20how%20we'll%20survive'%3A%20War-damaged%20Lebanese%20businesses%20face%20the%20unknown%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733538227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F66f0%2Flive%2Fef98f200-b40c-11ef-a0f2-fd81ae5962f4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcdd64v77491o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Traders%20and%20shop-owners%20lost%20their%20livelihoods%20as%20a%20result%20of%20destruction%20from%20Israeli%20attacks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A52%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcdd64v77491o%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcdd64v77491o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcdd64v77491o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22In%20Chhattisgarh%20Liquor%20Scam%20Arrest%2C%20Top%20Court%20Flags%20'Disturbing%20Features'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20flagged%20%26quot%3Bdisturbing%20features%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20arrest%20of%20former%20IAS%20officer%20Anil%20Tuteja%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20related%20to%20the%20alleged%20Chhattisgarh%20liquor%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20Abhay%20S%20Oka%20and%20Augustine%20George%20Masih%20termed%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20case%20as%20%26quot%3Bglaring%26quot%3B%20and%20recorded%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisturbing%20features%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20arrest%20of%20the%20former%20bureaucrat%20on%20April%2020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20petitioner%20(Anil%20Tuteja)%20on%20April%2020%2C%202024%2C%20at%20around%204.30%20pm%20was%20sitting%20in%20the%20ACB%20office%20at%20Raipur.%20Firstly%2C%20he%20was%20served%20summons%20directing%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20ED%20at%2012%20am.%20Thereafter%2C%20another%20summon%20was%20served%20while%20he%20was%20in%20the%20office%20of%20ACB%20calling%20upon%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20ED%20at%205.30%20pm.%20Thereafter%2C%20he%20was%20taken%20to%20the%20office%20of%20ED%20in%20a%20van%20brought%20by%20the%20ED%20and%20was%20interrogated%20throughout%20the%20night%20and%20arrested%20at%204%20am.%20The%20facts%20are%20glaring%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20underlined%20in%20its%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20allowed%20senior%20advocate%20Abhishek%20Manu%20Singhvi%20and%20other%20lawyers%20appearing%20for%20Tuteja%20to%20withdraw%20his%20appeal%20and%20granted%20him%20liberty%20to%20approach%20the%20trial%20court%20for%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SLPs%20are%20disposed%20of%20as%20withdrawn%20with%20liberty%20to%20apply%20for%20bail%20and%20if%20any%20such%20application%20are%20made%20considering%20the%20peculiar%20facts%20of%20the%20case%2C%20the%20special%20court%20concerned%20will%20give%20necessary%20priority%20in%20disposal%20of%20the%20bail%20application%2C%26quot%3B%20directed%20the%20bench.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditional%20Solicitor%20General%20S%20V%20Raju%2C%20representing%20the%20ED%2C%20informed%20the%20bench%20that%20the%20agency%20had%20to%20take%20remedial%20measures%20to%20ensure%20such%20incidents%20were%20avoided%20and%20there%20was%20a%20press%20release%20to%20this%20effect%20issued%20on%20October%2029%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20Singhvi%20said%20the%20top%20court%20previously%20quashed%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20registered%20by%20the%20ED%20on%20April%208%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20contended%20the%20ED%2C%20three%20days%20later%2C%20registered%20a%20new%20ECIR%20(complaint)%20based%20on%20the%20same%20set%20of%20facts%20and%20material%20saying%20the%20agency%20couldn't%20have%20new%20information%20in%20such%20a%20short%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%20asked%20if%20the%20ED%20could%20rely%20on%20the%20same%20material%20from%20the%20first%20ECIR%2C%20which%20had%20been%20quashed%2C%20to%20justify%20the%20registration%20of%20a%20second%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20submitted%20during%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20second%20ECIR%2C%20all%20relevant%20documents%2C%20including%20statements%20recorded%20under%20Section%2050%20of%20the%20PMLA%2C%202002%2C%20were%20obtained%20from%20the%20investigating%20officer%20of%20the%20first%20ECIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20the%20material%20collected%20remained%20on%20record%20and%20could%20form%20the%20basis%20of%20further%20proceedings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%20noted%20the%20quashing%20of%20the%20first%20ECIR%20was%20based%20on%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20predicate%20offence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20while%20it%20was%20not%20going%20into%20the%20legality%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20it%20wanted%20to%20see%20if%20the%20arrest%20was%20illegal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Oka%20then%20asked%20Singhvi%2C%20whether%20he%20wanted%20a%20detailed%20finding%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20saying%20it%20might%20have%20a%20bearing%20on%20the%20bail%2C%20if%20the%20court%20recorded%20its%20reasoning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESinghvi%20subsequently%20sought%20permission%20to%20withdraw%20the%20petition%20with%20a%20liberty%20to%20apply%20for%20bail%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20December%205%2C%20the%20top%20court%20expressed%20its%20displeasure%20over%20the%20ED%20hastening%20to%20arrest%20Tuteja%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20deplorable.%20How%20can%20you%20arrest%20a%20person%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%3F%20What%20is%20this%20happening%2C%20was%20it%20so%20urgent.%20You%20could%20have%20called%20him%20the%20next%20day.%20He%20was%20not%20some%20terrorist%20who%20would%20go%20in%20with%20bombs%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaju%20then%20tried%20to%20justify%20the%20agency's%20action%20saying%20there%20was%20an%20apprehension%20that%20Tuteja%20would%20go%20underground%20as%20he%20was%20avoiding%20its%20notices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20then%20told%20the%20ED%20to%20be%20prepared%20for%20answering%20the%20question%20on%20the%20maintainability%20of%20the%20fresh%20case%20filed%20by%20the%20agency%20on%20April%2011%20after%20the%20court%20set%20aside%20the%20entire%20ED%20proceedings%20against%20Tuteja%20and%20other%20accused%20on%20April%208%2C%20as%20the%20predicate%20offence%20was%20based%20on%20income%20tax%20proceedings%2C%20which%20was%20not%20a%20scheduled%20offence%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20has%20claimed%20the%20fresh%20case%20was%20based%20on%20the%20FIR%20registered%20by%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20police%20and%20on%20different%20charges%20and%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20claimed%20illegal%20profits%20worth%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20were%20earned%20by%20a%20syndicate%20involving%20politicians%2C%20bureaucrats%20and%20private%20individuals%20during%20the%20period%202019-23%20of%20which%20Tuteja%20was%20an%20integral%20part.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20this%20money%20allegedly%20came%20through%20bribes%20collected%20from%20distillers%20and%20unaccounted%20sale%20of%20country%20liquor%20by%20state-run%20liquor%20vends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%208%2C%20the%20top%20court%20quashed%20the%20money%20laundering%20case%20against%20Tuteja%20and%20his%20son%20Yash%20in%20the%20alleged%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%20liquor%20scam%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20saying%20there%20were%20no%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20was%20quashed%20after%20noting%20that%20since%20no%20ex-facie%20scheduled%20offence%20(main%20offence)%20existed%20against%20them%2C%20no%20offence%20under%20the%20PMLA%20was%20made%20out.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733538060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Frg3bppe_supreme-court_625x300_07_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fin-chhattisgarh-liquor-scam-arrest-top-court-flags-disturbing-features-7191399%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Friday%20flagged%20%26quot%3Bdisturbing%20features%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20arrest%20of%20former%20IAS%20officer%20Anil%20