A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fromanias-top-court-scraps-presidential-election%2Famp_articleshow%2F116062295.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gavaskar's%20Big%20Advice%20To%20India%20Bowlers%20In%202nd%20Aus%20Test%3A%20%26quot%3BHaven't%20Used...%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBatting%20great%20Sunil%20Gavaskar%20has%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%20with%20the%20Indian%20bowlers'%20lack%20of%20success%20with%20the%20pink%20ball%20on%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20Australia%2C%20saying%20they%20ought%20to%20have%20done%20better.%20Australia%20were%20comfortably%20placed%20at%2086%20for%20one%20at%20stumps%20after%20bowling%20out%20India%20for%20180%20in%20their%20first%20innings%2C%20thanks%20to%20pacer%20Mitchell%20Starc's%20six-wicket%20haul.%20Speaking%20on%20Star%20Sports%2C%20Gavaskar%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20have%20to%20make%20the%20batters%20play%20as%20much%20as%20they%20can.%20And%20this%20is%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20make%20the%20batters%20play%20as%20much%20as%20you%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20set%20them%20up%20by%20bowling%20a%20couple%20of%20deliveries%20outside%20and%20then%20get%20the%20ball%20to%20move%20back%20in%2C%20as%20it%20did%20to%20Nathan%20McSweeney%20in%20the%20Perth%20Test%2C%20or%20to%20Labuschagne%20in%20the%20Perth%20Test%2C%20like%20what%20Bumrah%20did.%20The%20Indian%20bowlers%20have%20not%20really%20used%20the%20pink%20ball%20as%20well%20as%20they%20should%20have.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20former%20Australia%20opener%20Matthew%20Hayden%20called%20Starc%20a%20%26quot%3Bmagician%20with%20the%20pink%20ball%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20left-arm%20quick%20ran%20through%20the%20Indian%20batting%20line-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarc%20was%20the%20wrecker-in-chief%20for%20Australia%20as%20he%20took%20six%20Indian%20wickets%20for%2048%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20the%20broadcaster%20about%20Starc%2C%20Hayden%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20has%20that%20scrambled%20seam%20delivery%20that%20goes%20across%20the%20right-hander%2C%20but%20when%20he%20does%20have%20that%20ability%20-%20which%20he%20did%20-%20I%20must%20admit%20I%20was%20a%20little%20surprised.%20I've%20never%20really%20seen%20the%20pink%20ball%20swing%20into%20the%20sort%20of%2040th%20over%20and%20so%20aggressively%20swing%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBy%20that%20stage%2C%20he%20used%20a%20really%20important%20word%2C%20and%20it's%20a%20bit%20of%20an%20underrated%20word%20as%20well%2C%20and%20that's%20'momentum'.%20It%20was%20all%20in%20favour%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20difficult%20position%20to%20come%20back%20from%20in%20life%20and%20sport%20is%20those%20opportunities%20to%20wrestle%20back%20momentum%2C%20and%20Mitchell%20Starc%20did%20that%20in%20only%20the%20way%20he%20can%20-%20when%20the%20lights%20are%20like%20the%20way%20they%20are%20and%20with%20that%20beautiful-coloured%20ball%20in%20his%20hand.%20He's%20just%20a%20magician%20with%20the%20pink%20ball.%26quot%3B%20Having%20reduced%20the%20visitors%20to%2082%20for%20four%20at%20tea%2C%20Australia%20took%20the%20remaining%20six%20wickets%20at%20the%20cost%20of%2098%20runs%20before%20dinner%20break%20was%20taken.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarc%20sizzled%20with%20his%20trademark%20inswingers%20to%20remove%20R%20Ashwin%20and%20Harshit%20Rana%20while%20Pat%20Cummins%20used%20the%20short%20ball%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProviding%20his%20take%20on%20Australia's%20bowling%20performance%20on%20day%20one%2C%20Hayden%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20Australia%20bowled%20in%20two%20halves%2C%20to%20be%20honest.%20I%20thought%20their%20first%20maybe%2020%20overs%2C%20they%20were%20very%20conservative.%20It%20was%20like%20they%20knew%20that%20the%20pink%20ball%20was%20going%20to%20start%20to%20swing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20when%20Scott%20Boland%20came%20around%20and%20just%20started%20getting%20into%20the%20line%20of%20the%20stumps%2C%20that%20was%20the%20turnaround.%20Around%20about%20that%2035th%20over%2C%20we%20saw%20some%20of%20those%20missiles%20that%20Mitchell%20Starc%20started.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20was%2045%2C%2050%20overs%20in%2C%20and%20it%20started%20to%20swing.%20That's%20what%20earned%20them%20the%20strong%20position%20they%20find%20themselves%20in%20today.%26quot%3B%20India's%20assistant%20coach%20also%20Ryan%20ten%20Doeschate%20also%20lauded%20Starc%20for%20his%20excellent%20display%20with%20the%20pink%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Ash's%20dismissal%20was%20a%20very%20good%20example%20of%20why%20he's%20so%20effective%20with%20the%20pink%20ball.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20ball%20swings%20back%20to%20a%20certain%20degree%2C%20a%20lesser%20degree%2C%20the%20batters%20can%20generally%20figure%20it%20out.%20But%20when%20you're%20guessing%20on%20both%20sides%2C%20it%20makes%20him%20far%20more%20effective.%20Just%20the%20areas%20he%20bowled%20today%20were%20superb.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20obviously%20he%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20confidence%20from%20the%20pink%20ball%2C%20having%20done%20well%20in%20the%20past.%20And%20he's%20probably%20the%20main%20exponent%20of%20swing%20bowling%20out%20of%20the%20two%20teams.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733537880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fbkm0lakg_cas_625x300_06_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsunil-gavaskars-big-advice-to-india-bowlers-in-2nd-australia-test-havent-used-7188895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sunil%20Gavaskar%20has%20expressed%20his%20disappointment%20with%20the%20Indian%20bowlers'%20lack%20of%20success%20with%20the%20pink%20ball%20on%20the%20opening%20day%20of%20the%20second%20Test%20against%20Australia%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A96%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fsunil-gavaskars-big-advice-to-india-bowlers-in-2nd-australia-test-havent-used-7188895%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We%20left%20corporate%20jobs%20and%20a%206-figure%20salary%20to%20travel%20full-time.%20It%20took%20years%20of%20saving.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Haley%20and%20Shane%20Mahabadi%20in%20a%20pool.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67538ffb8fbb2783ed306df7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHaley%20and%20Shane%20Mahabadi%20left%20corporate%20America%20and%20are%20traveling%20full%20time%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%3Cp%3EHaley%20and%20Shane%20Mahabadi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHaley%20and%20Shane%20Mahabadi%20left%20corporate%20jobs%20and%20a%20six-figure%20salary%20to%20travel%20full%20time.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20married%20couple%20planned%20and%20saved%20for%20years%20before%20heading%20to%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey're%20living%20on%20savings%20and%20some%20freelance%20work%20while%20exploring%20different%20income%20streams.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Haley%20and%20Shane%20Mahabadi%2C%20a%20married%20couple%20in%20their%20late%2020s%20who%20lived%20in%20Denver%20until%20August%20when%20they%20started%20traveling%20full-time%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%20Haley%20left%20her%20corporate%20job%20in%202023%20and%20Shane%20left%20his%20this%20year%20so%20they%20could%20travel.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaley%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20After%20graduating%20college%20in%202019%2C%20we%20did%20a%20two-and-a-half%20month-long%20backpacking%20trip%20through%20Southeast%20Asia.%20It%20was%20extremely%20life-changing%20and%20impactful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20of%20course%2C%20we%20had%20that%20tug%20of%20responsibility%20that%20brought%20us%20back%20to%20working%20and%20doing%20what%20everyone%20else%20was%20doing.%20We%20started%20working%20in%20corporate%20America%209-to-5%2C%20five%20days%20a%20week%2C%20no%20flexibility%2C%20no%20freedom%2C%20just%20feeling%20chained%20to%20the%20desk.%20And%20I%20just%20wondered%2C%20%26quot%3BIs%20this%20what%20the%20next%2040%20years%20is%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20started%20wondering%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20we%20could%20make%20traveling%20full%20time%20work%3F%26quot%3B%20After%20five%20years%20of%20daydreaming%2C%20planning%2C%20and%20saving%2C%20we%20made%20it%20happen%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20been%20traveling%20around%20Southeast%20Asia%20for%20over%20three%20months.%20We%20were%20in%20Indonesia%20for%20a%20month%2C%20Thailand%20for%20month%2C%20Vietnam%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%2C%20then%20the%20Philippines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20some%20of%20the%20most%20incredible%20adventures.%20We've%20met%20really%20interesting%20people.%20We've%20gotten%20to%20meet%20locals%20and%20try%20local%20cuisine%20and%20do%20all%20these%20things%20that%20we%20always%20were%20daydreaming%20about.%20So%20it's%20kind%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bpinch%20me%26quot%3B%20that%20we're%20actually%20out%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20just%20thought%2C%20if%20we%20never%20take%20this%20leap%2C%20I%20wonder%20if%2C%20when%20we're%20in%20our%20fifties%20and%20we'll%20look%20back%20and%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BWhy%20didn't%20we%20do%20that%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20kind%20of%20joke%20that%20we're%20pulling%20a%20year%20forward%20from%20retirement%20and%20traveling%20now%20while%20we're%20young%20and%20able.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22624fc252-db4f-4bb3-b7ff-d154888bf062%5C%22%3ELeaving%20a%20job%20with%20a%20six-figure%20salary%20was%20hard%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaley%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20In%202023%2C%20I%20was%20working%20as%20a%20creative%20director%20at%20a%20marketing%20agency%2C%20and%20I%20just%20found%20myself%20unhappy%20and%20feeling%20a%20little%20bit%20unfulfilled.%20I%20decided%20to%20quit%20my%20job%20to%20freelance%20and%20work%20my%20own%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20still%20able%20to%20work%20while%20traveling.%20For%20clients%2C%20I%20do%20social%20media%20management%20as%20well%20as%20photography%20and%20video%20creation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShane%20took%20a%20massive%20leap%20because%20he%20was%20getting%20a%20high-paying%20six-figure%20job%20in%20corporate%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Haley%20and%20Shane%20Mahabadi%20selfie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67538f994adc4cc134353539%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHaley%20and%20Shane%20Mahabadi%20left%20corporate%20America%20and%20are%20traveling%20full%20time%20in%20Southeast%20Asia.%3Cp%3EHaley%20and%20Shane%20Mahabadi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShane%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It%20was%20definitely%20scary%20to%20take%20the%20leap%20because%20I%20was%20doing%20well%20in%20my%20career%20and%20moving%20up%2C%20but%20we'd%20been%20fantasizing%20about%20it%20for%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20working%20as%20a%20manager%20of%20strategy%20and%20analytics%20at%20Dish%20Network%2C%20where%20I'd%20worked%20for%20about%20four%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20liked%20the%20role.%20I%20loved%20my%20team%2C%20loved%20the%20department%20I%20worked%20in.%20I%20guess%20the%20downside%20was%20it%20was%20just%20like%20an%20old-school%20job%20%E2%80%94%20five%20days%20a%20week%20in%20the%20office%2C%20not%20much%20flexibility.%20I%20wanted%20something%20that%20would%20allow%20me%20to%20travel%20more%20or%20work%20from%20other%20places.%20I%20thought%20if%20I%20don't%20do%20this%20now%2C%20before%20we%20probably%20start%20a%20family%2C%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20essentially%20impossible%20to%20do%20it%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20at%20work%20were%20sad%20to%20see%20me%20go%20but%20they%20were%20supportive.%20My%20boss%20offered%20to%20write%20a%20letter%20of%20recommendation%20and%20to%20help%20me%20when%20I%20want%20to%20reenter%20the%20workforce.%20That%20was%20a%20big%20relief%20to%20know%20that%20I%20have%20people%20on%20my%20side%20who%20can%20vouch%20for%20me%20that%20I%20was%20a%20good%20worker%20and%20I'm%20not%20just%20a%20crazy%20guy%20traveling%20the%20world%20without%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20come%20back%2C%20it%20might%20take%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20time%2C%20but%20I%20think%20I'll%20be%20able%20to%20find%20something%20eventually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20goal%20is%20to%20travel%20for%20a%20year.%20We're%20paying%20for%20it%20with%20savings%2C%20and%20then%20Haley's%20consistent%20stream%20of%20income.%20If%20something%20crazy%20happens%20and%20we're%20able%20to%20make%20a%20bunch%20of%20other%20streams%20of%20income%20that%20are%20doing%20really%20well%2C%20we%20could%20potentially%20extend%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20were%20planning%20I%20made%20a%20spreadsheet%20with%20roughly%20what%20I%20thought%20we%20would%20spend%20per%20day%20on%20hotels%2C%20food%2C%20activities%2C%20flights%2C%20and%20jotted%20it%20out%20from%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20saved%20our%20credit%20card%20miles%20for%20the%20past%20few%20years%2C%20so%20we%20really%20haven't%20had%20to%20spend%20money%20on%20any%20of%20the%20big%20international%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20so%20much%20lower%20here%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%20that%20you%20don't%20need%20quite%20as%20much%20saved%20or%20you%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20making%20as%20much%20to%20extend%20your%20time%20and%20travel%20for%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2240139a4c-286b-443d-af99-bb4fec74b5f6%5C%22%3EWe%20hope%20we%20can%20keep%20this%20flexibility%20forever%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHaley%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20don't%20plan%20to%20travel%20forever.%20We%20miss%20our%20families%20and%20community%20back%20home.%20But%20now%20I'm%20wondering%20how%20we%20can%20we%20make%20this%20flexibility%20work%20forever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20main%20priority%20right%20now%20is%20traveling%2C%20but%20we%20are%20also%20trying%20different%20things%20in%20our%20free%20time%20and%20seeing%20if%20we%20can%20create%20multiple%20streams%20of%20income%2C%20because%20even%20when%20we%20go%20back%20to%20the%20states%2C%20it%20would%20be%20amazing%20to%20continue%20to%20have%20a%20more%20flexible%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20been%20trying%20all%20these%20things%20that%20we%20probably%20wouldn't%20have%20if%20we%20didn't%20have%20all%20this%20free%20time.%20We've%20been%20hiking%2C%20swimming%2C%20snorkeling%2C%20scuba%20diving.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20did%20the%20Ha%20Giang%20Loop%20in%20Northern%20Vietnam.%20You%20motorbike%20for%20three%20days%20through%20the%20most%20incredible%20landscape%20you've%20ever%20seen.%20Just%20driving%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20motorbikes%20with%20the%20guide%2C%20wind%20in%20your%20hair%2C%20down%20winding%20mountain%20roads.%20You%20just%20felt%20like%20you%20were%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20in%20that%20moment%20I%20felt%20so%20glad%20we%20did%20this.%20There%20was%20not%20even%20a%20question%20in%20my%20body%20of%20regret.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShane%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDeciding%20to%20do%20this%20was%20hard%2C%20but%20one%20of%20the%20things%20that%20mentally%20helped%20me%20was%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWhat's%20the%20worst%20that%20can%20happen%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20worst%20that%20can%20happen%20is%20we're%20going%20to%20lose%20out%20on%20some%20amount%20of%20money%2C%20but%20we'll%20have%20traveled%20the%20world%20for%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20that%20bad%20of%20a%20worst-case%20scenario.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%