22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Famericas-got-talent-comedian-kabir-kabeezy-singh-dies-at-39-7191327%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Forests%20Ahead%2C%20Maoist%20Drones%20Above%3A%20How%20Poll%20Workers%20Keep%20Democracy%20Ticking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThey%20cross%20glaciers%2C%20lug%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20up%20mountains%20on%20their%20backs%2C%20and%20work%20in%20dangerous%20areas%20to%20ensure%20every%20last%20person%20can%20cast%20their%20ballot%20in%20the%20world's%20largest%20democracy.%20Polling%20booth%20workers%20have%2C%20fittingly%2C%20been%20honoured%20with%20the%20title%20of%20NTDV's%20Indian%20Of%20The%20Year%20in%20the%202024%20edition%20of%20the%20network's%20marquee%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReceiving%20the%20award%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20polling%20booth%20workers%20were%20Radha%2C%20a%20poll%20worker%20from%20the%20Velachery%20Assembly%20segment%20in%20South%20Chennai%2C%20Antiya%20Minz%2C%20a%20booth-level%20officer%20from%20Palamu%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20Rahila%20Rafique%20from%20Khansahib%20Assembly%20constituency%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20Suraj%20Singh%2C%20presiding%20officer%20from%20Losain%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20T%20Rama%20Rao%2C%20presiding%20officer%20from%20a%20booth%20in%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%2C%20Tikaish%20Kumar%20Sahu%2C%20presiding%20officer%20from%20Kanker%20district%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Chelo%20Lima%2C%20presiding%20officer%20from%20Itanagar%20in%20Arunachal%20Pradesh.%20The%20representatives%20included%20a%20transgender%20polling%20officer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20challenges%20that%20polling%20workers%20face%20while%20organising%20elections%2C%20Mr%20Sahu%2C%20who%20was%20working%20in%20Kanker%20district%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20said%20they%20trekked%20through%20dense%20jungles%20and%20had%20Maoist%20drones%20hovering%20above%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BConducting%20elections%20in%20our%20polling%20booth%20is%20fairly%20challenging.%20We%20had%20to%20leave%20home%20three%20days%20before%20the%20elections%20and%20were%20dropped%20to%20a%20Border%20Security%20Force%20(BSF)%20camp%20in%20a%20helicopter.%20We%20then%20had%20to%20trudge%20through%20dense%20jungles%20for%205%20km%20to%20reach%20the%20booth.%20When%20we%20were%20walking%20to%20the%20booth%2C%20we%20could%20see%20Maoist%20drones%20observing%20us%20from%20above.%20But%20we%20had%20security%20cover%20and%20we%20managed%20to%20conduct%20the%20election%20successfully%2C%20registering%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%2071%20per%20cent%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAntiya%20Minz%20from%20Palamu%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20who%20also%20helped%20conduct%20elections%20in%20an%20area%20affected%20by%20Maoist%20violence%2C%20said%20she%20and%20her%20colleagues%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20educating%20villagers%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20their%20right%20to%20vote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20travel%2020%20km%20to%20reach%20the%20booth%20and%20cross%20streams%20using%20all%20available%20means%2C%20including%20tractors%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoats%2C%20Helping%20Tribals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresiding%20Officer%20T%20Rama%20Rao%20from%20the%20Andaman%20and%20Nicobar%20Islands%20and%20his%20colleagues%20had%20to%20use%20a%20boat%20to%20get%20to%20their%20polling%20station%20in%20Dugong%20Creek.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20face%20challenging%20terrain%20and%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20reach%20polling%20booths%20but%20the%20administration%20and%20the%20Election%20Commission%20helped%20us.%20The%20area%20is%20home%20to%20the%20particularly%20vulnerable%20Onge%20tribe.%20I%20already%20worked%20as%20a%20teacher%20in%20a%20school%20in%20the%20area%20and%20the%20administration%20and%20tribal%20welfare%20department%20helped%20us%20reach%20every%20tribe.%20They%20don't%20have%20much%20experience%20casting%20votes%20because%20they%20only%20do%20so%20for%20general%20elections.%20Voting%20using%20EVMs%20is%20also%20a%20tough%20task%20for%20them.%20But%20we%20saw%20a%20voter%20turnout%20of%2094%25%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Inclusion%20Key%20To%20Democracy'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETransgender%20polling%20officer%20M%20Radha%20from%20Chennai%20said%20inclusion%20is%20key%20to%20a%20successful%20democracy%20and%20that%20she%20has%20been%20working%20to%20ensure%20that%20more%20transgender%20voters%20exercise%20their%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20provides%20equal%20voting%20rights%20to%20all%20and%20the%20inclusion%20of%20transgender%20voters%20has%20become%20the%20need%20of%20the%20hour%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuraj%20Singh%20was%20part%20of%20a%20polling%20party%20that%20had%20to%20trek%2017%20km%20to%20get%20to%20their%20booth%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Losain%2C%20crossing%20forests%20and%20glaciers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20to%20cross%20glaciers%20and%20pass%20through%20areas%20with%20sliding%20zones%20and%20shooting%20stones.%20Snow%20was%20falling%20and%20there%20was%20no%20electricity%20in%20our%20booth.%20Language%20was%20also%20a%20challenge%2C%20but%20we%20still%20managed%20to%20conduct%20polling%20successfully%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733537040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fed15mokg_poll-booth-workers-indian-of-the-year_625x300_06_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fndtv-indian-of-the-year-5-km-trek-through-forest-maoist-drones-above-how-poll-officers-keep-indian-democracy-ticking-7189793%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22They%20cross%20glaciers%2C%20lug%20electronic%20voting%20machines%20up%20mountains%20on%20their%20backs%2C%20and%20work%20in%20dangerous%20areas%20to%20e