al%20bad%20actor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECAA%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftop-influencer-agents-managers-database-youtube-instagram-tiktok%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleading%20Hollywood%20talent%20agency%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20digital%20arm%20that%20represents%20influencers%20on%20YouTube%2C%20Instagram%2C%20and%20TikTok.%20The%20agency%20works%20with%20creators%20to%20monetize%20their%20followings%20through%20brand%20partnerships%2C%20consumer%20products%2C%20and%20other%20business%20ventures.%20CAA%20is%20not%20named%20as%20a%20defendant%20in%20the%20suit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWineberg%2C%20and%20to%20a%20lesser%20extent%20Graham%2C%20used%20the%20company's%20earnings%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20de%20facto%20personal%20piggy%20bank%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20suit%20alleges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Franta%2C%20in%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20said%20Lindsay%20Wineberg%20%26amp%3B%20Associates%20%E2%80%94%20Heard%20Well's%20business%20manager%20and%20accountant%2C%20led%20by%20Jeremy%20Wineberg's%20father%20%E2%80%94%20acted%20negligently%20by%20turning%20the%20other%20cheek%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20in%20doing%20so%20negligently%20facilitated%20the%20draining%20of%20over%20%241%20million%20of%20company%20monies%20into%20the%20personal%20pockets%20of%20Wineberg%20(and%20Graham).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBryan%20Sullivan%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Jeremy%20Wineberg%20and%20Lindsay%20Wineberg%20%26amp%3B%20Associates%2C%20said%20the%20allegations%20aren't%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20Connor%20Franta%20is%20without%20merit%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement.%20Sullivan%20said%20his%20clients%20never%20%26quot%3Bengaged%20in%20any%20misconduct.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20intend%20to%20pursue%20all%20of%20our%20rights%20and%20expect%20to%20be%20vindicated%20in%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20Sullivan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Shenk%2C%20a%20lawyer%20for%20Graham