ing%20organic%20mangoes%20through%20Sreshte%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20selecting%20farmers%2C%20the%20couple%20carries%20out%20detailed%20research%20to%20verify%20that%20they%20adhere%20to%20the%20standards%20for%20organic%20farming.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20personally%20inspect%20the%20soil%20and%20confirm%20that%20no%20pesticides%20or%20chemicals%20are%20used.%20Once%20we%20verify%20that%20they%20follow%20genuine%20organic%20methods%2C%20we%20establish%20our%20requirements%20and%20build%20a%20lasting%20relationship.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20vital%20that%20the%20farmers%20are%20government-certified%20and%20trained%20under%20the%20Subash%20Palekar%20Natural%20Farming%20method%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Pavani.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20strictly%20insist%20on%20the%20use%20of%20herbal%20pesticides%20like%20neem%20astra%20and%20brahmastra%2C%20and%20fertilisers%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Ejeevamrutham%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Eghana%20jeevamrutham%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F302506%2Fmadurai-organic-farmer-makes-cow-dung-artefacts-natural-ecofriendly-recyclable%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emade%20from%20cow%20dung%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20cow%20urine%2C%20and%20natural%20jaggery.%20We%20only%20support%20farming%20that%20avoids%20chemicals%2C%20helping%20our%20farmers%20grow%20crops%20in%20the%20most%20environmentally%20friendly%20way%20possible%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EVenturing%20into%20%E2%80%98ready-to-eat%E2%80%99%20items%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20ensure%20greater%20control%20over%20the%20quality%20and%20authenticity%20of%20their%20products%2C%20Sreshte%20expanded%20its%20operations%20by%20setting%20up%20a%20dedicated%20processing%20unit%20and%20warehouse%20in%20Manikanta%E2%80%9