st%20300%20were%20regular%2C%E2%80%9D%20Srishti%20admits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20lockdown%20measures%20eased%2C%20SABIA%20managed%20to%20set%20up%20community%20spaces%20and%20adapt%20to%20the%20situation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20set%20up%20a%20library%20space%20in%20my%20own%20home%2C%20and%20later%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Jaipur%2C%20I%20opened%20a%20home%20library%20there%20too.%20This%20space%20was%20able%20to%20keep%20children%20engaged%20in%20learning%20even%20when%20their%20school%20had%20shut%20down%20due%20to%20the%20pandemic%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Srishti%2C%20recounting%20the%20story%20of%20Anita%20and%20Rani%20%E2%80%94%20two%20girls%20who%2C%20despite%20being%20out%20of%20school%20for%20years%20due%20to%20COVID%2C%20were%20able%20to%20catch%20up%20because%20they%20had%20a%20supportive%20learning%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%202760px)%20100vw%2C%202760px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20girls%20standing%20in%20front%20of%20newly%20set%20up%20bookshelves%20in%20their%20school.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525.jpg%202760w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-768x577.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRepublicDay_Nithari-1_11zon-1732781525-1536x1153.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FRe