D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20was%20a%20pivotal%20revelation%20for%20Jyoti.%20She%20had%20been%20searching%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20daughter%E2%80%99s%20struggles%2C%20only%20to%20realise%20that%20the%20problem%20had%20been%20the%20milk%20all%20along!%20%E2%80%9CPackaged%20and%20processed%20milk%20is%20a%20bad%20option%20for%20her%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20local%20dairy%20farms%20fell%20short%20due%20to%20hygiene%20issues%20or%20subpar%20feed%20given%20to%20cows.%20Resolving%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20Jyoti%2C%20a%20textile%20engineering%20graduate%2C%20embarked%20on%20a%20self-learning%20journey.%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20farming%20background.%20All%20that%20I%20have%20implemented%20is%20through%20trial-and-error%20and%20self-learning%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJyoti%20set%20up%20her%20first%20farm%20in%20Lucknow%20with%2015%20mixed-breed%20cows%2C%20including%20Jerseys%20and%20Sahiwals.%20However%2C%20her%20limited%20knowledge%20of%20cow%20nutrition%20affected%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20milk.%20After%20relocating%20to%20Thane%2C%20Jyoti%20identified%20a%20pressing%20need%20for%20pure%20A2%20cow%20milk%20in%20urban%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CI%20grew%20up%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20where%20getting%20fresh%20milk%20was%20never%20a%20worry.%20When%20my%20daughter%20needed%20pure%20milk%20here%2C%20I%20realised%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20necessity%2C%20not%20a%20luxury%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20a%20research%20study%20published%20in%20the%20National%20Library%20of%20Medicine%2C%20A2%20milk%20%E2%80%94%20milk%20that%20only%20contains%20a%20variant%20of%20beta-casein%20called%20A2%20%E2%80%94%20has%20on%20several%20occasions%20proved%