%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20measures%20taken%20by%20the%20city%20have%20lowered%20the%20levels%20of%20particulate%20matter%20and%20made%20it%20more%20livable%20and%20sustainable.%20One%20of%20the%20most%20innovative%20strategies%20in%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20fight%20against%20air%20pollution%20is%20the%20%E2%80%98superblock%E2%80%99%20concept.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20urban%20planning%20approach%20divides%20city%20streets%20into%20octagonal%20blocks.%20Inside%20these%20blocks%2C%20only%20pedestrians%2C%20cyclists%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F381023%2Fbhubaneswar-odisha-best-public-transport-india-crut-sustainable-urban-mobility%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epublic%20transport%20%3C%2Fa%3Eare%20allowed%2C%20while%20cars%20can%20only%20use%20the%20outer%20streets.%20This%20reduces%20traffic%2C%20lowers%20vehicle%20emissions%2C%20and%20improves%20air%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201024px)%20100vw%2C%201024px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20view%20of%20Barcelona%20showcasing%20its%20superblocks%2C%20with%20green%20spaces%20and%20pedestrian-friendly%20streets%20within%20the%20octagonal%20city%20blocks.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-300x146.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-500x244.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-768x374.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fbarcelona11_11zon-1732804640-150x73.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-384042%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESuperblocks%20are%20octagonal%20city%20blocks%20for%20pedestrians%2C%20cyclists%2C%20and%20public%20transport%2C%20with%20cars%20restricted%20to%20outer%20streets%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E(Representational%20image)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20of%20the%20main%20causes%20of%20air%20pollution%20that%20contribute%20almost%2050%25%20are%20vehicular%20emissions%2C%20industrial%20activities%2C%20construction%2C%20garbage%20burning%2C%20and%20emissions%20from%20homes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Jha%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Barcelona%2C%20each%20superblock%20covers%20an%20area%20of%20400%C3%97400%20metres%2C%20which%20is%20larger%20than%20a%20city%20block%20but%20smaller%20than%20a%20neighbourhood.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20create%20more%20space%20for%20public%20use%2C%20help%20biodiversity%2C%20promote%20sustainable%20transportation%2C%20and%20even%20encourage%20social%20interactions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20concept%20of%20superblocks%20was%20introduced%20in%20Barcelona%20as%20part%20of%20its%202013-2018%20Urban%20Mobility%20Plan%2C%20which%20aimed%20to%20redo%20120%20intersections.%20Currently%2C%20the%20city%20is%20working%20on%20redesigning%20one-third%20of%20the%20streets%20in%20the%20L%E2%80%99Eixample%20district%2C%20originally%20planned%20by%20Ildefons%20Cerd%C3%A0.%20Starting%20in%202022%2C%20the%20city%20is%20focusing%20on%20remodelling%2021%20streets%20by%202030.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20reliable%20EV%20infrastructure%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20component%20of%20Barcelona%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20is%20its%20focus%20on%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noo